# .prism — {{PROJECT_NAME}}

This project is **Prism-aware**. The `.prism/` directory holds the structured-workflow artifacts that keep the project wired into the Prism/Griot ecosystem.

Run `/prism-init` (or `python init_prism.py`) to scaffold the full structure:

```
.prism/
├── shared/          # committed — research, plans, validation, brainstorms, designs
│   ├── research/    # YYYY-MM-DD-topic.md
│   ├── plans/       # YYYY-MM-DD-feature.md
│   └── validation/  # YYYY-MM-DD-report.md
└── local/           # gitignored — personal notes
```

See the Prism plugin for the full workflow: **research → plan → implement → validate**.
